  "remarks": "TAi.155 Key commander in the Haqqani Network (TE.H.12.12.) under Sirajuddin Jallaloudine Haqqani (TI.H.144.07.). Taliban Shadow Governor for Orgun District, Paktika Province as of early 2010. Operated a training camp for non-Afghan fighters in Paktika Province. Has been involved in the transport of weapons to Afghanistan.; Listing: Listed by the UN 1988 Committee on 4 October 2011 (amended on 29 Nov. 2011 and 22 April 2013)",
